  <div class="container">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Honest scope</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">Who does what when a notice arrives.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">A clean line between the books work we do and the response and representation only a licensed professional can do.</p>
